1. *Spavam* u svojoj postelji svaki dan. (I sleep in my bed every day.)
2. Ujutro se *spavati* ne želi. (In the morning I don't want to sleep.)
3. On će *spavati* do podne. (He will sleep until noon.)
4. Ona je *spavala* najduže od svih. (She slept the longest of everyone.)
5. *Spavali* smo do 2 ujutru. (We slept until 2 am.)
6. Beba je *spavala* površno. (The baby was sleeping lightly.)
7. Njegovi roditelji su se *spavali* u dnevnoj sobi. (His parents were sleeping in the living room.)